Class AppointmentView

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Appointment
      • model.AppointmentView
  • public class AppointmentView
extends Appointment
    AppointmentView class POJO for appointmentsview tableview in database. Used for populating the Table in the Mainscreen of the application. Used for displaying the Customer and Contact names instead of IDs.
